  "release_notes": "Dropped the in-activity drift introduced in 1.0.50. The smooth sin-wave wander made the figure visibly slide around while stretching, jumping jacks, doing weights, and dancing — looked twitchy rather than lively. Stationary moves now stay anchored at their spot for the full duration of each pose, the way real exercise looks. Cartwheel is unchanged (it was never given drift since the cartwheel motion is intrinsic). Spots themselves are still randomized per play via _random_spots, so the figure still visits different cross-canvas locations each Ready click — it just holds still once it gets there.",
